=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>(3)<span> </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span>实现当俯仰角的角度值位于<span lang=\"EN-US\">-80~-10</span>度间时，直流电机正转，直流电机的转速随着倾角的增大而增大，随着倾角的减小而减慢；（<span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span>分）<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>(4)<span> </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span>实现当俯仰角的角度值位于<span lang=\"EN-US\">10~80</span>度间时，直流电机反转，直流电机的转速随着倾角的增大而增大，随着倾角的减小而减慢；（<span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span>分）<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>(5)<span> </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span>实现当滚转角的角度值小于<span lang=\"EN-US\">-10</span>度时，电机<span lang=\"EN-US\">A</span>停止转动，电机<span lang=\"EN-US\">B</span>的转速和转向随着俯仰角的变化而变化；（<span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span>分）<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>(6)<span> </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span>当滚转角的角度值大于<span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span>度时，电机<span lang=\"EN-US\">B</span>停止转动，电机<span lang=\"EN-US\">A</span>的转速和转向随着俯仰角的变化而变化。（<span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span>分）<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><br></p>","userAnswer":null,"analyzeContent":"","analyzeVideo":null,"subjectId":null,"examDots":"26,","previousId":405,"sprintId":null,"subjectNumber":null,"difficultyLevel":null,"images":null,"weType":0,"wxAnswerType":null,"isMySubject":null}]}}